bhale jodi ( kannada : ಭಲೇ &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 1970 indian kannada language drama film written and directed by y. r. swamy . it stars rajkumar in dual roles with bharathi and dinesh in other lead roles . the film was based on the story written by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; seetharaman and was produced under rajkamal arts banner . the movie was remade in telugu in 1972 as &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; bullodu and in hindi in 1973 as jaise ko taisa .